Repoint rv_tester's external deps (cvm, CoreArchChecker, mem-manager) from the
internal aus-gitlab GitLab archives to their public github.com/tenstorrent
mirrors so the tree builds outside Tenstorrent's network.

- cvm / CoreArchChecker: same pinned commit, github .tar.gz archive + sha256.
  The github archive top-level dir for cvm is "CVM-<commit>", so strip_prefix
  is updated to match.
- mem-manager: internal pin is not published; re-pinned to the public HEAD
  (7775edbd) with the matching github .tar.gz sha256. The lz4 BUILD patch still
  applies cleanly.

--- a/bazel/external_deps.bzl
+++ b/bazel/external_deps.bzl
@@ -40,20 +40,20 @@
